{"tid":1248823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"暫時最佳策略一定係 圍 然後等政府自己癱瘓","createTime":"2019-06-21T14:27:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T14:40:06.000Z","uid":135891,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"72f07a02207149f47b41f6200acd703e11f85c9e","tid":1248823,"uid":135891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:27:41.000Z","msg":"貿貿然攻又話出師無名又話冇光環<br />\n<br />\n好似而家咁 立會開會就圍立會等佢取消會議<br />\n政府唔回應就圍政總等佢自己閂門<br />\n警犬打人就圍警總等佢冇得收工<br />\n咁多政府部門 總之達唔到五大要求就圍到佢自己收皮<br />\n<br />\n你放軟手腳咪大家鬥消極戰 比更多空間文宣組同外交部打心理戰打國際民意<br />\n<br />\n佢忍唔住打人到時就大條道理升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ac04f433c6d4905da1d316d22731a14b4052b0","tid":1248823,"uid":135891,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:29:43.000Z","msg":"我地攰 尾班車就散<br />\n佢地就一肚氣"},{"pid":"c016fae638c31138ce9e7b2967bf26d02ec8b62c","tid":1248823,"uid":135891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:30:34.000Z","msg":"不受傷 不被捕"},{"pid":"9f4373b459be2d892f36857cd453ab7102ba6ea6","tid":1248823,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:33:43.000Z","msg":"覺得可行<br />\n和理非得黎同雨革完全唔同<br />\n而且人數唔洗多，打游擊就得<br />\n可以番shift<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af912f5d5f611ff03529b637d5c64e7a81acb1a1","tid":1248823,"uid":135891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:35:05.000Z","msg":"話知佢空城計定萬人屌老母 總知癱瘓政府運作"},{"pid":"c6d82415d5a403205cc1f386b67cd1803451e74d","tid":1248823,"uid":135891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f4373b459be2d892f36857cd453ab7102ba6ea6","tid":1248823,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:33:43.000Z","msg":"覺得可行<br />\n和理非得黎同雨革完全唔同<br />\n而且人數唔洗多，打游擊就得<br />\n可以番shift<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:40:06.000Z","msg":"佢著哂甲一攻就由義士保護後面走 盞佢地自己攰<br />\n佢地宿我